<li><a href="Reel-to-reel_audio_tape_recording" title="Reel-to-reel audio tape recording">Reel-to-reel tape</a> (1940s)</li>
<li><a href="SoundScriber" title="SoundScriber">SoundScriber</a> (1945)</li>
<li><a href="Gray_Audograph" title="Gray Audograph">Gray Audograph</a> (1945)</li>
<li><a href="Dictabelt" title="Dictabelt">Dictabelt</a> (1947)</li>
<li><a href="LP_record" title="LP record">LP record</a> (1948)</li>
<li><a href="Gramophone_record" title="Gramophone record">45 rpm record</a> (1949)</li>
<li><a href="Ribs_(recordings)" title="Ribs (recordings)">On-the-ribs recordings</a> (late 1940s)</li>
<li><a href="RCA_tape_cartridge" title="RCA tape cartridge">RCA tape cartridge</a> (1958)</li>
<li><a href="Fidelipac" title="Fidelipac">Fidelipac</a> (1959)</li>
<li><a href="Stereo-Pak" title="Stereo-Pak">Stereo-Pak</a> (1962)</li>
<li><a href="Compact_Cassette" title="Compact Cassette">Compact Cassette</a> (1963)</li>
<li><a href="8-track_tape" title="8-track tape">8-track</a> (1964)</li>
<li><a href="PlayTape" title="PlayTape">PlayTape</a> (1966)</li>
<li><a href="Mini-Cassette" title="Mini-Cassette">Mini-Cassette</a> (1967)</li>
<li><a href="Microcassette" title="Microcassette">Microcassette</a> (1969)</li>
<li><a href="Steno-Cassette" title="Steno-Cassette">Steno-Cassette</a> (1971)</li>
<li><a href="Elcaset" title="Elcaset">Elcaset</a> (1976)</li>
<li><a href="Cassette_single" title="Cassette single">Cassette single</a> (1980)</li>
<li><a href="Picocassette" title="Picocassette">Picocassette</a> (1985)</li>
</ul>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px">
<td></td>
</tr>
